@nurmerey I don't understand why you'd use `render_to_temporary_file` to do that, it's an utility function that simply renders a Django template to a file, it doesn't do any work related to the PDF conversion.

You should instead use [`render_pdf_from_template`](https://github.com/incuna/django-wkhtmltopdf/blob/e7aa62484a6cbe89a3eeb155fcc8aef31d615cff/wkhtmltopdf/utils.py#L151).

